Interface Parseable

      • handleTurtle

        void handleTurtle(Turtle workTurtle,
                java.lang.String[] args)
                  throws java.lang.Exception
        Does all the needed changes to the Turtle.
        Parameters:
        workTurtle - The turtle that should be altered
        args - The line of code which should be executed
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - If an error occurs it throws either ParserNotFoundException, SyntaxErrorException, VariableAlreadyInUseException or VariableNotFoundException.
